text.section:
In developing the criteria for citizen involvement projects or corporate sponsorship projects, the Trust may consider activities that:
Preserve water quality and habitat;
Restore aquatic and land resources;
Publish or produce educational materials on the Chesapeake Bay and other aquatic and land resources of the State;
Provide educational scholarships or training; or
Promote conservation programs for the Chesapeake Bay and other aquatic and land resources of the State through the media or other means.
